{"tid":450386,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"義肢矯形主管東院跳樓亡","createTime":"2017-10-28T06:39:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-28T08:01:07.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"11f9f6fc9ab466bb91641eb2d0adf915d928e813","tid":450386,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T06:39:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171028/20196958\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171028%2F20196958&d=ttNQWDG3zbjj93Fe4ww0CZnkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=3696b3f8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171028%2F20196958&h=c02097f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171028/20196958</a><br />\n<br />\n義肢矯形主管東院跳樓亡<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n0:00<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】柴灣東區醫院矯形及創傷外科主管鄭子傑，昨日在醫院墮樓身亡，消息指鄭近日曾向朋友透露因工作壓力感不開心。<br />\n<br />\n49歲的鄭子傑，擔任東區醫院矯形及創傷外科主管，與家人住在愉景灣。昨下午2時許，警方接報指一名男子重傷倒卧東區醫院精神科宿舍「樂民居」對開山坡，消防員到場證實他已死亡，警方懷疑他由天台墮下。死訊傳出，醫院同事傷心不已，東區醫院行政總監劉楚釗醫生亦到場視察。義肢矯形師屬醫管局的專職醫療人員，現時醫管局轄下各區聯網都設義肢矯形服務。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171028/large/a0802a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171028%2Flarge%2Fa0802a.gif&h=e5fc061a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n東院矯形及創傷外科主管鄭子傑（小圖）倒卧醫院宿舍山坡，消防員到場證實鄭死亡。劉柏麟攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n疑受工作壓力困擾<br />\n<br />\n消息稱，鄭子傑任職義肢矯形師近20年，在行內以手藝純熟及細心見稱，近年出任東區醫院矯形及創傷外科主管後，較多處理管理及行政工作，只有高難度義肢才親自出手，他近日曾透露受到工作壓力困擾。<br />\n<br />\n本港著名截肢跑手馮錦雄與鄭子傑相交逾10年，對好友去世感到震驚。他指鄭多次參加毅行者及長跑等比賽，予人印象陽光，早年亦與鄭組隊參加毅行者。他稱鄭手藝數一數二，亦是香港截肢者協會顧問。他稱讚鄭是行內少有用心製義肢的技師。東區醫院證實死者為該院職員，稱對事件深表哀痛，會盡力協助和支援其家屬及部門職員。<br />\n<br />\n■記者劉柏麟、關英傑"},{"pid":"1538cf72507d6c0a8a25cbaadb48140e7ebe71b6","tid":450386,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T06:40:16.000Z","msg":"醫生都跳 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9725ed3ad23e3b993ce06f640bc812d520a51280","tid":450386,"uid":126100,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T06:43:49.000Z","msg":"適合做醫生唔適合玩人事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nR.I.P.<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f611b21b84c9f008b2da7b46a6b558f77c08343","tid":450386,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T06:47:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>適合做醫生唔適合玩人事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nR.I.P.<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔想做行政，<br />\n做返醫生咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b13fe1f80b31c26be281a30bfdae605f668dd30","tid":450386,"uid":77637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T06:50:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>適合做醫生唔適合玩人事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nR.I.P.<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢都唔係醫生<br />\n係義肢部"},{"pid":"253f7d0d792b59900cbaf7cf4b78e2c21c052b74","tid":450386,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T06:59:54.000Z","msg":"義肢部壓力大到要跳樓？<br />\n<br />\n香港好多人都要跳"},{"pid":"c8b96fbd6f6a73fdce6dfb9e1b9c8f63484ce252","tid":450386,"uid":35774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T07:01:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>醫生都跳 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nallied health嚟"},{"pid":"a67f79163970952bac02879cdba2954353209664","tid":450386,"uid":115910,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T07:01:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>義肢部壓力大到要跳樓？<br />\n<br />\n香港好多人都要跳</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係呀你跳撚左未"},{"pid":"